{{wikipediapar|Primer (disambiguation)}}
==English==
===Noun===
{{en-noun-reg}}

# A textbook formerly used in [[Wikipedia:primary education|primary education]] to teach the alphabet and other basic concepts.
#{{biology}} A single-stranded nucleic acid molecule required for the [[Wikipedia:DNA_replication|initiation of replication]] of a [[DNA]] molecule.
# Any substance used to start a [[fire]].
# A small [[charge]] that explodes when struck with force that [[ignite]]s the [[gunpowder]] in [[ammunition]].
# A layer of [[paint]] designed to underlay a [[topcoat]], used to enhance the [[adhesion]] and [[durability]] of the topcoat and help in protection of the surface.
# A device used to circulate [[gasoline]] into the ignition chamber of an engine.

